"Murriah": "Huh? I don't look well? Is that so?"
"...I know, perhaps you can assist me with something. Do you have some time?"
"What do you say to taking them out in my stead?"
"I understand, it's something I should do myself... But I just can't. That's why I've asked you."
"I see, you must be very busy. If you ever find you have the time, please reconsider."
